import React from 'react';
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import { Grid, Button, TextField } from '@mui/material';

export default function ExploreS() {

    return (
        <Box textAlign='center' style={{ margin : 16, padding: 16, position:'relative'}}>
            <TextField fullWidth  variant="standard" label="이메일,ID 또는 할 일 검색" /> 
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
                <Grid xs={4} md={4} item >
                    <Button 
                        style={{position:'relative', top: '-85px',  fontSize: '14px', fontWeight: '600', color: '#111'}} >
                        검색
                    </Button>  
                </Grid>
                <Grid xs={4} md={4} item >
                    <Button 
                    style={{position:'relative', top: '-85px',  fontSize: '14px', fontWeight: '600', color: '#111'}} >
                        팔로워
                    </Button>    
                </Grid>
                <Grid xs={4} md={4} item >
                    <Button 
                    style={{position:'relative', top: '-85px',  fontSize: '14px', fontWeight: '600', color: '#111'}} >
                        팔로잉
                    </Button>    
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Box>
    );
}
